name: HAS_SELECTOR()
documentation: Returns Y or N according to the existence of the selector property or auto-selector

name: IS_SELECTOR_HIDDEN()
documentation: Returns Y if the selector is hidden from presentation, N otherwise

name: DATAGROUP_TO_INCREMENT()
documentation: The control data group for the current table

name: NUMBER_OF_PAGES()
documentation: The number of pages to display for the current table

name: CURRENT_PAGE()
documentation: The current page being displayed in the current table

name: START_ROW()
documentation: The start row being displayed for the current table

name: END_ROW()
documentation: The end row being displayed for the current table

name: TABLE_PAGE_ACTION()
documentation: The JavaScript to use for changing table page

name: PREV_TABLE_PAGE_ACTION()
documentation: The JavaScript to use for changing to the previous table page

name: NEXT_TABLE_PAGE_ACTION()
documentation: The JavaScript to use for changing to the next table page

name: FIRST_TABLE_PAGE_ACTION()
documentation: The JavaScript to use for changing to the first table page

name: LAST_TABLE_PAGE_ACTION()
documentation: The JavaScript to use for changing to the last table page
